  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    Coronavirus (COVID-19): test kits for schools and FE providers
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  

  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">Guidance for schools and further education (FE) providers on the initial supply of coronavirus (COVID-19) home testing kits for pupils, teachers and staff.</p>

  </div>
</div>

