    Published 26 August 2020
    <br></br>Last updated 14 October 2020
      <a href="#full-history" class="app-c-published-dates__toggle govuk-link" data-controls="full-history" data-expanded="false" data-toggled-text="- hide all updates">+ show all updates</a>
      <div class="app-c-published-dates__change-history js-hidden" id="full-history">
        <ol>
            <li class="app-c-published-dates__change-item">
              <time class="app-c-published-dates__change-date timestamp" datetime="2020-10-14T10:55:08.000+01:00">14 October 2020</time>
              <p class="app-c-published-dates__change-note">Updated the 'Making an order for additional coronavirus tests' with additional information for schools and FE providers in particularly high risk areas who may be eligible for an additional delivery of test kits.</p>
            </li>
            <li class="app-c-published-dates__change-item">
              <time class="app-c-published-dates__change-date timestamp" datetime="2020-10-07T15:39:00.000+01:00">7 October 2020</time>
              <p class="app-c-published-dates__change-note">Updated to provide further information on the distribution of test kits for symptomatic staff and how schools and FE providers can look up their unique organisation number (if they have not received it).</p>
            </li>
            <li class="app-c-published-dates__change-item">
              <time class="app-c-published-dates__change-date timestamp" datetime="2020-09-22T18:03:19.000+01:00">22 September 2020</time>
              <p class="app-c-published-dates__change-note">Updated content to confirm that schools and FE providers ordering additional test kits will be provided with one box of 10 kits per 1,000 pupils or students.</p>
            </li>
            <li class="app-c-published-dates__change-item">
              <time class="app-c-published-dates__change-date timestamp" datetime="2020-09-14T19:09:12.000+01:00">14 September 2020</time>
              <p class="app-c-published-dates__change-note">Updated information on ordering test kits and clarification of wording for different age group test use.</p>
            </li>
            <li class="app-c-published-dates__change-item">
              <time class="app-c-published-dates__change-date timestamp" datetime="2020-08-26T18:51:00.000+01:00">26 August 2020</time>
              <p class="app-c-published-dates__change-note">First published.</p>
            </li>
        </ol>
